![](/assets/2015-09-09-the_human_mortality_explorer/hmdexp.png)
*https://jschoeley.shinyapps.io/hmdexp*

My first project after arriving at [Max-Planck Odense Center on the Biodemography of Aging](http://www.sdu.dk/en/om_sdu/institutter_centre/maxo): The [Human Mortality Explorer](https://jschoeley.shinyapps.io/hmdexp).

Visualizing the risk of dying across age and time around the globe. Compare countries with each other and dig into the gender gap of mortality risk. Build with [R](https://www.r-project.org/) + [shiny](http://shiny.rstudio.com/) and not possible without the [Human Mortality Database](http://www.mortality.org/).

The source code (without data) is available at <https://github.com/jschoeley/hmdexp>.

